project

Class Layer

  • java.lang.Object
    • project.Layer

  • public class Layer
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a layer in the Canvas and acts as a wrapper for a GraphicElement. A Layer can be visible or invisible.
    See Also:
    Canvas, GraphicElement
